There's a tonal quality to the videos featuring Andrew and Brittany as 
siblings, that indicates the promising nature of Buzzfeed's motion picture 
venture.

The key exists in highlighting different tonal approaches to Buzzfeed 
videos: confessional reactions when participants are interviewed or try 
things, heightened comedic theatricality for lifestyle re-enactments, and a 
more versatile, nuanced acting approach for the motion picture releases.

Overall, Buzzfeed seems to focus on creating video content designed to 
examine the multi-faceted experience of living life in the modern world.
